Living at his friend's place, unemployed... to make the disaster complete, he brought his girlfriend with him. The guy was incredibly lucky to pick our agency. I gave him a job and took care of our mediation fee. He hesitated a little but soon was kneeling on the floor with his mouth full. Unfortunately, he wasn't such a slut I thought he would be. The guy refused to get fucked but agreed to fuck me instead. So, I got fucked by a lumberjack with a big dick. That's still pretty sweet...
title: Dirty Scout 229
